---
title: Birria-Style Cheesy Beef Tacos with Consommé Dipper
description: Birria – a spicy, fragrant Mexican meat stew – is said to have originated in Jalisco, then famously became a taco in Tijuana! We've packed ours with juicy beef and smoky chipotle, and served with a savoury, spiced consommé for dipping!
